{"product_id":"honeysticks-super-jumbos-6pk","title":"Honeysticks Beeswax Crayons Super Jumbos 6pk","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW231400276 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"OutlineElement Ltr SCXW89954478 BCX8\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eBig, bold, and made for little hands – \u003cstrong\u003eHoneysticks Beeswax Crayons Super Jumbos 6pk\u003c\/strong\u003e are a perfect next step in your toddler’s creative journey. These super-sized crayons help build grip strength and coordination, making them ideal for curious creators aged 1 and up.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eSuper-sized for little hands: \u003c\/strong\u003eAt 10cm long and 2cm thick, these chunky crayons are easy to hold and hard to break – perfect for building early drawing confidence.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eNo nasties, just pure creativity: \u003c\/strong\u003eCrafted using 100% pure New Zealand beeswax and food-grade colours. No paraffin wax, no fillers, no worries.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eBetter for them, better for the planet:\u003c\/strong\u003e With sustainably sourced beeswax and natural + non-toxic ingredients, Honeysticks are gentle on little ones and the earth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cstrong\u003eHandcrafted by families, for families:\u003c\/strong\u003e Designed by parents who believe in a better way to play, Honeysticks Super Jumbos are lovingly handmade in New Zealand to encourage creative expression from the very first scribble. \u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eNow, in our refreshed Honeysticks look – welcome to a world of pure creation.\u003c\/strong\u003e\u003c\/em\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Honeysticks UK","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":56350549705085,"sku":"HCRSJ6","price":14.95,"currency_code":"GBP","in_stock":true}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/file